<i>What power within
allows him to give his life</i>

59:43.623 --> 59:47.961
<i>to preserve his land and the lives
of the families who work it?</i>

59:50.380 --> 59:52.883
<i>It can only be love.</i>

59:55.135 --> 59:59.514
<i>It will not be written
that the Lord Odda saved Wessex,</i>

59:59.681 --> 01:00:03.185
<i>but that is the story I will tell.</i>

01:00:03.310 --> 01:00:07.355
<i>That he gave his life
