01:00:15.363 --> 01:00:17.949
<i>Sigefrid had been defeated.</i>

01:00:18.074 --> 01:00:24.456
<i>But Alfred knew as well as I
that the Danes were sure to return.</i>

01:00:25.290 --> 01:00:28.627
